text: Light & Bright Skagit Highlands home, ready for new owners! Spacious open-concept main floor plan boasting tall ceilings, laminate flooring, a spacious living room, open dining area, and the kitchen with a breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. Upstairs is a versatile family/flex area, perfect for a home gym or office! Shared full bath, conveniently-located laundry, and 4 bedrooms including the expansive primary suite with walk-in closet and 5-piece ensuite with lovely mountain views. Fully-fenced backyard with a covered patio, open patio, and plenty of room for hobbies and entertaining. Attached garage, community park/playground, located near shops, restaurants, parks, the Skagit River, and commuter routes. Welcome Home!

Discover serene living with this single-level, light-filled, 3-bed rambler in the heart of Gibralter. Allow nature to delight you while enjoying panoramic bay, mountain, and Deception Pass State Park views from the expansive back deck. The spacious interior and flowing floor plan features endless vistas from one end to the other. Cook gourmet meals in the open kitchen with island and eating nook overlooking the bay. Large primary suite with walk-in closet and 5-piece en suite bath with jetted tub. Encapsulated by a manicured lawn and garden beds, the outdoor enjoyment is endless. Large 3-car garage. The cherry on top: private beach access, moorage, and tideland rights provide a lifestyle enriched with natural beauty and bayside allure.

This enchanting 1900's farm house will capture your heart. From the moment you arrive, you will feel a sense of serenity and connection with nature. Set on a sunny, level .87-acre lot, gardeners will enjoy reaping what they sow from their private orchard, veggie and flower gardens. This spacious 4 bed + den home is flooded with natural light. It has been mindfully updated over the years, yet retains period charm. Main level primary bed with en-suite 3/4 bath and walk-in-closet. Large, open kitchen with eat-up bar and gas range. Home office is in a quiet corner of the main level. Store ALL of your toys and tools in the 1400+ sft detached garage with HUGE shop. Darling hobby/potting shed. Host Tulip Festival parties on the entertainment deck.

Excellent craftsman style home in the sought after Gateway Heights neighborhood of Sedro Woolley. Backing up to highly desirable green space allowing you to create your own little oasis. This home is conveniently located near hiking trails & parks. Cozy living room greets you w/ warm fireplace for those chilly PNW days, leading into the tactfully located kitchen w/ granite counters & stainless appliances overlooking the deck & large yard. Follow the stairs to the upper level where three bedrooms are located. The primary offers ample space, walk in closet & an en-suite bathroom complete w/ double vanity & window, allowing natural light in during the day. W/D are conveniently located on the second level as well. Don't miss this great home!

This charming home offers comfort and convenience with 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. The downstairs bedroom presents versatility, serving as either a office space or bedroom. Upstairs, you'll find the practicality of a dedicated laundry room, along with 3 additional bedrooms and 2 full bath. Entertaining is a breeze with the dining room conveniently situated adjacent to the back deck, offering seamless indoor-outdoor flow for gatherings. Tranquility of cul-de-sac living, free from the disruptions of through traffic. Moreover, the home's unique setting backing to a green belt with a creek ensures privacy and peace. For outdoor enthusiasts, the proximity to Kulshan Trail just steps away provides easy access to nature and recreational activities.

Come home to this updated home in Park Village, one of Skagit County's most popular 55+ parks. The roomy floor plan allows for entertaining, and both bedrooms have direct bathroom access. Updates include newer vinyl plank flooring and fresh paint inside, roof re-coated with Eterna-Kote silicone roof coating approximately two years ago, and a stand-alone gas stove in addition to the forced air furnace. The lot includes two storage buildings and backs up to greenbelt. The park has easy access to transit, shopping and medical services, with a refreshed clubhouse and RV parking available. Some furniture available with sale, ask for details.

Welcome to Anchor Cove Marina, gateway to the San Juan Islands! This awesome 40' covered slip allows up to a 45' vessel and has nearly 17' of bridge clearance. Situated on the outer end of C dock, this slip offers you great views of Mt Baker, Guemes, Cypress and Blakely islands without even leaving the dock! There is a fish and crab cleaning station right there too! Anchor Cove is gated and includes a nice shop with tools equipment for you to use, along with laundry, showers, crab cookers, barbecues, picnic tables and more. There's also some additional parking for boats on trailers. Anchor Cove is conveniently located near downtown Anacortes, yet just a short cruise and you're in the beautiful San Juan islands!
nearby_schools: Northwest Educational Service District 189, Anacortes School District

text: Welcome to this charming home featuring a complete MIL apartment w/ separate entrance! Main floor features: Living room w/ cozy wood fireplace, formal dining room, kitchen w/ marble countertops & gas stove top, huge laundry room w/ tons of cupboard space, primary bedroom w/ spacious closet & primary 3/4 bath w/ custom tile shower surround, full bath & two additional bedrooms. Downstairs features: Spacious bonus room for entertaining w/ French doors leading outside & separated MIL apartment w/ 1 bedroom + bonus room, kitchen, living room, & full bath. Ample storage throughout home & brand new hot water heater. Outside: Huge four car garage and newly fully fenced backyard. Close to I-5, Skagit river park, shopping & dining.

New construction triplex! 3 separate units, ranging from 1500 to 1609 sqft, each with a single car garage. Each unit is 3 bedroom and 2.5 baths. LVP flooring and stainless steel kitchen appliances. Laundry appliances included. Fenced and irrigated front yards, alley access to garage. Very walkable to services and community amenities. Subdivision is complete and units can be sold separately at a future date. 1119 West unit and 1117 center unit are already rented!

Welcome to 2510 Briarwood Circle where the charm of this 3 bed 2 bath rambler is immediately apparent upon arrival. The covered front porch invites you into a space where light and warmth abound. Cooks will love the cozy yet functional eat in kitchen, equipped with stainless-steel appliances and a gas range. The southern exposure of this property bathes the interior in natural light creating a light and bright living space. A 2 car garage and spacious driveway offer ample parking and storage solutions. Entertainment and relaxation opportunities are endless with a fully fenced backyard, large side deck for gatherings, and a garden shed to house all your outdoor tools. Perfect location with easy access to parks, schools and the YMCA.

Wonderful opportunity to create your very own PNW oasis in the heart of Cape Horn area. This property is just waiting for your vision. From building, to potentially creating personal hobby & recreational areas, to simply enjoying the surrounding topography. The options abound!

If you are looking for the dream view lot - this is it. Located in the Fee Simple area of Shelter Bay (where you own the land) this lot has all of the amenties of the area (marina and golf course) with the additional Eagle's Nest private secluded beach! The lot has been surveyed and house plans are available. 90% of the work has been completed for permitting including geo-tech study, survey lines and critical set back. Drive up to the hilltop view area that is perfect for your dream home. Utilities in the street including water, sewer and power. Potential Owner Financing with strong terms.

INVESTOR ALERT! Affordable Home In The Country on corner lot, 2 Bdrm, 1 Bath Home. Propane Wall Heater, Over 3/4 Acre W/Mature Trees And Shrubs. Home needs work and lot needs clean-up. Being sold AS-IS Condition.

Magnificent residence in the premier 55+ community of Woodside, w/views of community park & greenbelt! Extraordinary design loaded with upgrades, including Central AC! Light filled open living & dining on main w/gleaming hardwood, corner gas FP & vaulted ceilings. Superb kitchen w/loads of storage & counter space, stainless, granite & cook island w/seating. Primary on Main w/walk-in, featuring CA closet system, elegant ensuite bath w/tiled shower & dual vanity. Office/Study off entry w/custom built-ins. Full daylight lower w/huge bonus room, 2 guest beds, full guest bath, plus huge storage area. Main level covered entertainment deck, lower-level patio area & serene backyard. Clubhouse, Bocce Ball Ct, trails & parks. HOA cares for landscape!

SUNRISE VIEWS OVER THE MOUNTAINS AND WATER - straight off your deck! This property boasts space, privacy, main-story living, 2nd kitchen & detached shop! Located on stunning Fidalgo Island, you'll love the breathtaking sights of Similk Bay, the Cascade Mountains, Mt. Baker, and even Mt. Rainier on a clear day. This 2, 521 sqft home sits on over 1/2 acre, has attached 2-car garage, main level primary suite, gigantic deck for outdoor entertaining & soaking in the views. Downstairs has 2nd kitchen and bonus room, 2 bedrooms, patio off sliding glass doors, large utility room. Detached shop has additional 1-car garage door, wood stove, large storage room w/2-way exterior access. Several mature & producing cherry and fig trees. As-is sale.

Beautiful setting as you look out over these two flat parcels on nearly 8.5 acres surrounded by the up close & breathtaking mountains. Great access off Hwy 20 abutting Birdsview Meadows Lane. Fantastic opportunity for your dream home, horses, farm or agriculture. Nearby Skagit River & Rasar State Park in the foothills of Mt. Baker. Two parcels included: P42687 and P42344. All old structures/buildings have been removed; start fresh with your vision for this special property.

Attention spec builders and self-build contractors! This vacant land on Fir Lane in Glenhaven Lakes is a golden opportunity for your next project. Nestled between established homes on a quiet street, this partially sloped lot boasts mature trees, good sunlight, and prime access to community amenities such as heated pool, lakes and clubhouse. Whether you're looking to craft a dream home for yourself or seeking an investment opportunity, this parcel offers the ideal foundation. With its serene location and community perks, seize the chance to build something exceptional in the heart of Glenhaven Lakes.

3 bedroom, 2 story, adorable home in a great location close to the YMCA, shopping, medical facilities, schools and a community playground. This home has been well maintained, offers 1301 s/f, a spacious primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and an upgraded shower. Natural gas heating and hot water. The 3 bedrooms & 1.75 baths are on the upper level and 1/2 guest bath on the main. Fully fenced back yard is perfect for your pets. The back yard abuts a greenbelt for complete privacy.

Burlington Cedar Point 55+ Condominiums. Great location and close to dining, shopping, parks, schools and I-5 access. Immaculate, interior newly painted, one level 1240 sq ft condominium with attached 528 sq ft garage. RV parking available $25/mo. Nice sized bedrooms both with attached baths and walk in closets. Light and bright with lots of natural light, hardwood floors in dining, kitchen and living. Covered front entry porch and covered rear deck. Gas fireplace and gas furnace with air conditioning. Vaulted ceiling in living room amplifies space and well-lit high ceiling in kitchen great amenity. Laundry rm & extra pantry off kitchen. Peninsula bar and dining eating space. HOA dues are $400 per month. Well maintained!

Lovely single level 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in desirable Clearidge neighborhood. Private courtyard entrance. Situated on a quiet cul-de-sac, the home features a tastefully updated kitchen with stainless appliances, granite countertops, tile backsplash and large island/eating bar. Open to the spacious dining room, it's offers a great area for gatherings. Sliding doors in dining room and french doors in master bedroom open to the expansive deck with gazebo and large, beautifully landscaped backyard with sprinkler system. Cozy living room features vaulted ceilings and a gas log fireplace. 2 car garage with huge storage overhead. Custom roomy shed with electricity and RV parking are added features. Top of the line blinds accent the windows.

Awesome North facing home with stunning Skagit Valley views and sunsets. One level rambler with an open floorplan on 5 level usable acres in the desirable Conway area. Fantastic kitchen with large island and seating for 5. Newly updated main bathroom with beautiful tiled shower. Two car attached garage, large carport, and a detached 36 x 50 heated shop with a bathroom. RV parking and septic hookups. Plenty of space for it all!

This beautiful split-level floor plan has been meticulously maintained! Main floor features a spacious living room with a wood burning fireplace. Dining room looks over the large deck & backyard. Spotless cook's kitchen includes all appliances and white cupboards. The primary bedroom features a 3/4 bath . The other 2 bedrooms are just down the hall from another full bath. Lower level opens to a finished bonus room with a cozy wood fireplace insert and 2nd backyard/garage access. Stepping out, you'll find beautiful landscaping, a patio hot tub ready , & a 12''X16' shop with power for all your tools or hobbies. Storage is abundant in the home as well as the detached shop.

Expansive water views from this stately home in the Sunset Cove Estates. Enjoy the ever-changing marine boat traffic views. Main level gives you a living room, dining area, kitchen with eating space, family room, plus private primary suite with soaking tub, dual head shower and large Walkin in closet. Bonus room with bathroom upstairs plus, fully finished lower level includes 2nd kitchen, 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, office & family room. Heated garage with 43ft bay, workbench, 240amp, wired for generator. Entertain on your new multi-space stone patios. Property located on quiet cul-de-sac with private path to WA Park trails, gazebo, picnic area, boat ramp & beach. WA State Ferry out to the San Juan Islands & Skyline Marina moments away.

This Sedro-Woolley home checks all the boxes! Three bedrooms and one and three quarter baths with desirable layout optimizing space and privacy. Primary bedroom with private bath including newer shower unit install and walk-in closet. Large living room open to kitchen with eating space, appliances stay and are just one year old. Fully fenced backyard with storage shed, overlooking neighboring Christmas tree farm below. Backyard patio for entertaining. Other features include forced air furnace and A/C unit, LVP flooring, fresh interior paint, roof is just one year old. Playground park located just across the street! Home has been preinspected and is sure to go fast!

Welcome Home to this light filled 3 bed, 2 bath home with attached 2 car garage located back off main road perfectly set in Sedro Woolley! With fresh interior paint throughout this home checks all the boxes, Living room and Family room both have fireplaces, spacious kitchen with lots of cabinets and counter space. Large primary bedroom that offers your own en suite. Enjoy the privacy of large fully fenced yard with Covered front and back porch with a plenty of room for BBQs and gatherings Nice wood soffits and plenty of room for RV parking. Dont let this one pass its 1st time on market since it was custom built.

INVESTOR ALERT! This under construction home is situated on 1.73 acres with over 100 ft. of riverfront. This home is a canvas for your finishing and personal touches with major upgrades done: all new siding, windows, re-leveled, re-structured roof w/new cross beams, Zip System sheathing (R-9), electrical panel (200 amps), and much, much more. Outdoor amenities include partially fenced pasture, barn w/electrical, chicken coop, RV/boat parking, and a riverfront fishing shack. All above the floodplain! This great investment opportunity awaits, schedule a showing today! Previous Buyer got Cold Feet

Custom newer built rambler on 3 level acres, first time on market! Located on a cul-de-sac, in a private community, bordered by 40 acres of Skagit Land Trust where the elk & deer roam free. Front door opens to an open concept kitchen, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a huge island, vaulted ceilings, wood burning stove & incredible natural lighting. Massive primary bedroom features: a walk-in closet & access to covered porch with stunning views. Primary bathroom features: custom tile work, double sink & granite countertop. Spacious additional bedrooms connect with charming full bath. Utility room with ample storage. Fully fenced, ready for you to bring your pets & animals! 3 car garage is 1, 000 sq ft: wired for welder & RV.

Nestled within the Pressentin Creek neighborhood, this charming home offers a serene .58-acre level lot. Large 1782 square-foot manufactured home has 3 beds, 2 baths with a office/den. Open living room into dinning and kitchen. This home sits on a full concrete slab foundation with concrete blocking. Metal roof makes it perfectly low maintenance. Ample room for RVs, boats, and more, right on your property along with a wood shed and kennel for a dog. No flood insurance needed here!

Pride in ownership is an understatement for this meticulous mountain retreat. Tucked into the North Cascades Mountains, or the American Alps, this picturesque single-level house & 762 sq ft ADU has everything for idyllic country living. Custom built 3-bd, 2-bth main house w/newer bamboo flooring, plus a fully permitted ADU, w/bonus finished space above for a bdrm or office. Both structures have brand new roofs, cedar siding & are wired for generators. New 25kW Grid-tied solar array, designed to fully offset electrical needs + new heat pump/AC. Private Skagit River beach access through HOA. Spacious yard, beautiful landscaping & established garden. Opportunities for this quality of homestead on 5+ acres are rare. Don't miss your chance!

Welcome home to this Gem! LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION! This 3-bed, 2.5-bath and BONUS ROOM! in the vibrant Skagit Highlands Community offers a functional floor plan situated on a spacious corner lot. Enjoy living amidst nature's beauty, with trails and parks just steps away. Conveniently located close to amenities, mountain views and more! This is the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Don't miss out on this idyllic retreat your dream lifestyle awaits!

Wonderful newly refreshed home close to parks, schools and easy access to I-5. Brand new quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and new flooring throughout the home. Downstairs boasts tall 10-foot ceilings. Living room overlooks the fenced-in backyard that has been newly leveled and seeded for grass. Great size primary room with vaulted ceilings attached bathroom with double sinks and a walk-in closet. Home has a long driveway with plenty of parking and a 2-car attached garage.

Located in the premier development of Saratoga Passage. Breathtaking views of Skagit Flats and Olympic Peninsula from this beautiful lot. Enjoy ever-changing quilt-work of Skagit Valley farmland. Wake up to sunrises spotlighting snow-capped Olympic Mountains. Relax to glorious sunsets. Located in much sought-after Conway school district & 3 minutes from I-5. This beautiful level lot is ready for your dream home!
